title: James Band - Its harder to land than to crash but its mostly the
description:
James Band - Rocks on so many levels

James Band mates their influences from rock, jazz, classical music and metal with their undying love for the 70&#039;s classic rock band tradition. Their capricious and spontaneous approach to music finished with a touch of Norwegian ethnicity rekindles the spirit of the golden age of rock in the new millennium. Get ready to experience Norway&#039;s best kept secret!
